data.description: Gorgeous 3 bedroom home, all with en suite bathrooms, and a bonus room on the 3rd floor, in the sought after gated neighborhood of Martinique. This West Indies inspired home offers custom lighting, beautiful hardwood floors, builder upgrades, and upscale characteristics. The first floor bedroom has plenty of room to relax, and features a full bathroom with a walk-in shower. Upstairs the spacious master bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and a stunning master bath that has double sinks, a large soaker tub, and separate walk-in shower. The 3rd bedroom upstairs has great closet space, a large balcony, and full bathroom with a large bathtub/stand up shower.On the third floor you'll find an additional room that could be used for entertaining, or relaxing on the attached balcony watching the sunset over North Lagoon.This home has a kitchen that is sure to bring out the chef in you. It features stainless steel appliances, a double oven, custom wood cabinets with glass doors, a breakfast bar, granite countertops, farmhouse sink, and is open to the oversized living room area. The living area flows out into a serenely landscaped courtyard. This is a wonderful space for entertaining friends and family, with lots of privacy. This home also has a large laundry room with an access to the courtyard, as well as an oversized one car garage.This prestigious neighborhood was designed to preserve nature, and live among it. The neighborhood includes open greens, natural walking trails that lead to local marinas, boat storage, and amazing restaurants. Just a few amenities include a peaceful community pool, ponds, playgrounds, and a basketball court. Martinique is only a short distance away from the state park and beach! Walking distance to some of the best restaurants including Captain Anderson's and Grand Marlin.
